tr.th: Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us

tr.td: The results show mildly elevated HbA1c and fasting glucose, indicating impaired glucose metabolism or possible early diabetes. Renal function, electrolytes, and other parameters are within normal limits. Recommend clinical correlation and consideration of further evaluation or management for glycemic control.
